data.title: Something besides hospital food
data.text: Daughter was in the hospital and wanted something besides hospital food.  We decided to go to Subway.  Food was delivered promptly and the way it was ordered.  Ordered a dozen cookies and she acted like we had asked for a million dollars.  Dumped them into the container and crammed the lid on them.  Will get in car and drive to a different subway before I go back to this one.
